'''Clay''' is a resource that can be found by tilling dirt, sand, or [[Artifact Spot]]s, by mining [[Mining#Clay Node|Clay Nodes]] at the [[Ginger Island#Dig Site|Ginger Island Dig Site]], or from cracking open [[Minerals#Geodes|Geodes]]. It can also be received as a gift from [[Jas]] or [[Vincent]] at the [[Feast of the Winter Star]].

