==Bundles==
Clay is not used in any [[Bundles|bundles]].

==Tailoring==
Clay is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create a [[Tailoring#Shirts|Shirt]]. [[File:Shirt001.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
Two, three, or five Clay may be requested by several fish in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].
==Tips==
* It may be worth considering digging for clay in [[the Mines]], as this will additionally produce [[Cave Carrot]]s. [[Bomb]]s or other explosives can be used to dig the dirt faster.

==History==
{{History|1.3.27|Added [[Garden Pot]].}}
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].  Can be requested in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].}}
{{History|1.5|Used as an ingredient to the Fiber Seeds, Deluxe Retaining Soil, and Bone Mill recipes. Can now be dropped by Clay Nodes.}}

